				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C3%8Dch/D%E1%BA%A1-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-Th%E1%BB%A5-H%C3%A0ng-th%C3%A0nh-v%C4%83n-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Bch-H%E1%BB%93i-Nh%E1%BA%A1c-phong-ti%E1%BB%81n-sa-t%E1%BB%B1-tuy%E1%BA%BFt/poem-IgDSgJQjAgj84F6KHzeoxQ">Dạ thướng Thụ Hàng thành văn địch (Hồi Nhạc phong tiền sa tự tuyết) - 夜上受降城聞笛（回樂峰前沙似雪）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C3%8Dch/author-WesEXQEj_Uo-QKdZcJ784w">Lý Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Du-Nam-Hoa-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-2NjeSPREpEDyFiS_9M_k2Q">Du Nam Hoa tự - 遊南華寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Linh/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Ph%C3%B9-Phong-ch%E1%BB%A7-nh%C3%A2n-%C4%91%C3%A1p/poem-JIfVl-3ILF4CeMtEfeNxgA">Đại Phù Phong chủ nhân đáp - 代扶風主人答</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Linh/author-Q_JpPOHTIyzNkB76eQk-WQ">Vương Xương Linh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-Vu-Nh%E1%BB%AF-T%C3%ADch-Du-Gi%C3%A1ng-Th%C3%A1nh-qu%C3%A1n/poem-P4cU40cpbHwtHCC3Xrn7lg">Đồng Vu Nhữ Tích “Du Giáng Thánh quán” - 同于汝錫遊降聖觀</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/author-Xw0ALUMVQ06c4vUGFngNbA">Vương Kiến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/H%E1%BB%93-gi%C3%A0-th%E1%BA%ADp-b%C3%A1t-ph%C3%A1ch-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-01-ph%C3%A1ch/poem-ckVrrZFkNNGZTFO-W9K3Yw">Hồ già thập bát phách - đệ 01 phách - 胡笳十八拍－第一拍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/author-EhbmJp2hi9HLiXQfO6maGA">Thái Diễm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Kh%E1%BA%A9u-h%C3%A0o-t%E1%BA%B7ng-tr%C6%B0ng-qu%C3%A2n-L%C6%B0-H%E1%BB%93ng-th%E1%BB%AD-c%C3%B4ng-th%C3%AC-b%E1%BB%8B-tri%E1%BB%87u/poem-N2yAzp4GxC6bvsCmWOP2IA">Khẩu hào tặng trưng quân Lư Hồng, thử công thì bị triệu - 口號贈徵君廬鴻，此公時被召</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A1n/poem-gmqFq5Zpfzxx1-YxTAGHqw">Nguyên đán - 元旦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/author-mhAlF-W1JHQDMsH_S0aV3Q">Hà Như</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/Song-ng%C6%B0-h%C3%AD-thu%E1%BB%B7/poem-fRRxPR5rlnhsFpBjDx_klA">Song ngư hí thuỷ - 雙魚戲水</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/author-c6g39E3xPTFyf_DWOB-GYw">Bùi Dương Lịch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/V%C4%83n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-1/poem-Y_1v6AFY7WGa1-WstaBhBw">Văn Vương 1 - 文王 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-Huy-B%C3%ADch/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-O16EucYpffiGXP-5vZoklg">Vô đề kỳ 2 - 無題其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-Huy-B%C3%ADch/author-IUtlhs85uNhJ4NvGicsgMg">Bùi Huy Bích</a>)<br></div>	</div>
